        <description>&lt;img src="http://localhost:1313/p/batworthy-and-chagford-common/map.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Batworthy and Chagford Common" /&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;information&#34;&gt;Information
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Distance: &lt;b&gt;
3 miles&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; Grade: &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/tags/gentle/&#34;&gt;Gentle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; A GPX route of this walk is available: &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/gpx/batworthy-and-chagford-common.gpx&#34;&gt;Download GPX &lt;svg  xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;  width=&#34;24&#34;  height=&#34;24&#34;  viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;  fill=&#34;none&#34;  stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34;  stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;  stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;  stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;  class=&#34;icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-download&#34;&gt;&lt;path stroke=&#34;none&#34; d=&#34;M0 0h24v24H0z&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M4 17v2a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-2&#34; /&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M7 11l5 5l5 -5&#34; /&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M12 4l0 12&#34; /&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.google.com/maps/dir/?api=1&amp;destination=50.66321%2c-3.89451&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Directions to Car Park  &lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; class=&#34;icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-directions&#34;&gt;
